trong> 一样，放进去容易取出来难。</p>\n<p>所以想整个 <strong>知识库系统</strong> ，这个项目倒是容易找个来抄抄改改，就是服务器比较麻烦，目前自己用的是 1 核 2 GiB 的 <strong>阿里乞丐版</strong> 。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"阿里乞丐版 1\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://images.gitee.com/uploads/images/2021/0329/082028_dcfcc1aa_7404663.png\"/></p>\n<p>有个问题就是这挂壁服务器老是内存 99.99%，而且一直给我推有安全风险。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"阿里乞丐版 2\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://images.gitee.com/uploads/images/2021/0329/082458_b339ba89_7404663.png\"/></p>\n<p>想问下 V2 的大佬们，用啥服务器比较稳定靠谱便宜实惠？或者这种情况要怎么处理啊？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1616977546, "replies": 48, "id": 766000}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1615112532", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1615112532", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 170754, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1615112532", "stars": 3196, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"username": "KrisZ", "website": null, "github": null, "psn": null, "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/72119a034c6883687ac3682f482c0d51?s=24&d=retro", "bio": null, "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/KrisZ", "tagline": null, "twitter": null, "created": 1532419396, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/72119a034c6883687ac3682f482c0d51?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/72119a034c6883687ac3682f482c0d51?s=24&d=retro", "location": null, "btc": null, "id": 335290}, "last_reply_by": "None123", "last_touched": 1617005307, "title": "今年 30 岁，想体验一次蹦极，想听一些过来人的经验", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/766085", "created": 1616987579, "content": "", "content_rendered": "", "last_modified": 1616987579, "replies": 45, "id"